{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/til2","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"0bdc5efe-6663-5927-bf94-5be931585756","html":"<p>라이브러리를 활용해 다양한 스크롤 애니메이션을 클래스 추가만으로 적용하기</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://wowjs.uk/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">WOW.js 사이트</a>에 연결된 <a href=\"https://github.com/graingert/wow\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">GitHub</a>에서 폴더 다운로드<br></li>\n<li>WOW-master/css/libs/animate.css 파일을 html 파일과 같은 폴더, 혹은 하위 폴더에 추가<br></li>\n<li>WOW-master/dist/wow.min.js 파일을 html 파일과 같은 폴더, 혹은 하위 폴더에 추가<br></li>\n<li>\n<p>스크롤 효과를 넣을 페이지 html 파일 header에 animate.css 파일 연결<br></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>link</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">rel</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>stylesheet<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>폴더/animate.css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<br>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>wow.min.js 파일 연결 및 실행 스크립트 추가</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>js/wow.min.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n<span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">WOW</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">init</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>스크롤 효과를 적용할 요소 클래스명을 “wow”로 지정<br></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>wow<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\nContent to Reveal Here\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://daneden.github.io/animate.css/?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Animate.css 웹사이트</a>에서 원하는 애니메이션 스타일을 골라 “wow” 클래스명 뒤에 추가<br></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>wow bounceInUp<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\nContent to Reveal Here\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>기본 세팅값으로는 웹페이지 최초 로딩 후 한 번만 작동하니, 애니메이션 효과 반복 실행을 위해서는 advanced option 적용 필요.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>data-wow-duration: 애니메이션이 실행(지속)되는 시간 설정<br></li>\n<li>data-wow-delay: 페이지 로딩 후 애니메이션이 실행되기까지 간격 설정<br></li>\n<li>data-wow-offset: 요소가 어느 정도 올라왔을 때 애니메이션이 실행될지 지정<br></li>\n<li>\n<p>data-wow-iteration: 애니메이션 반복 횟수 설정<br></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>section</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>wow slideInLeft<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">data-wow-duration</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>2s<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">data-wow-delay</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>5s<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>section</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>wow slideInRight<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">data-wow-offset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>10<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>  <span class=\"token attr-name\">data-wow-iteration</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>10<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/til2","tagSlugs":["/tag/til/","/tag/javascript/","/tag/css/","/tag/html/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-04-15T16:13:32.160Z","description":"페이지에 스크롤 애니메이션 쉽게 적용하기","tags":["til","javascript","css","html"],"title":"WOW.js를 이용하여 다양한 스크롤 애니메이션 적용하기","socialImage":"/naon.png"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/til2"}}}